<section xml:id="topic-creating-a-feature-branch" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" >
  <title>Creating a Feature Branch</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>
      When you set out to make changes to the project you will do so by working on a feature branch.
      <xref ref="fig-create-feature-branch-and-switch" /> illustrates the process of creating a feature branch.
      The activities in this section will walk you through the process of creating a feature branch on which you will fix the issue that you claimed in <xref provisional="a reference back to ch2-issue-tracker section" />.
    </p>
  </introduction>

  <p>
    <figure xml:id="fig-create-feature-branch-and-switch">
      <caption> Create feature branch. </caption>
      <image source="images/ch-upstreaming-changes/create-feature-branch-and-switch.png" width="75%">
        <description>
          Cloud image of origin, upstream, and local branches.
        </description>
      </image>
    </figure>
  </p>

